{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_02_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 1話 ライブ前のひと時",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏フェスの本番直前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Right before the summer festival",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さて、みんな準備は出来たかな……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope everyone is ready—huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8333333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 7.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ふはははは！　遅いっ！\nてやっ、てやーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha! Too slow!\nTake this! Take that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.966666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 13.866666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "この声は……芽衣か？\nライブ直前に何をしてるんだか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that… Mei’s voice?\nWhat’s she doing‚ right before the concert?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 20.733333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "あははっ、すずにゃんびっしょびしょだった～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hahaha‚ you’re soaked‚ Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 25.133333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さーん！\nえへへー、みんなで水遊びしてたんだー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}!\nHehe. We’re having a bit of a water fight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.166666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんでまた本番直前にそんなことを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right before you go on stage?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.666666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 35.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ん～なんだかみんなカチンコチンだなって思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone was looking kinda stiff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、今日は\nいつもより会話が少なかった気がするな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚\neveryone did seem less chatty than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 45.86666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！\nみーんな顔もがっちがちなんだもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right!\nEveryone had such stiff looks on their faces.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 50.666666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんの顔をぐにぐにーってしたら\nお返しされちゃった、あははっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I gave Suzu-nyan a tug on the cheek‚\nand she gave me one right back! Hahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 58.06666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "ま、みんなが緊張するのも分かるよ\n新曲は今までの月ストにない雰囲気だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand the tension‚ of course.\nOur new song is a departure for Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 66.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんなにどう思われるか考えちゃうよなーって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It makes you wonder what all the fans will think!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……確かにな。みんなで頑張って作った分\n不安も大きいんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Sure. All that hard work of writing it yourselves\nintensifies the hope it will pay off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 77.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "でもさ、頑張れるだけ頑張ったんだし\n本番前にあれこれ考えてもしょうがないと思うんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we’ve done the best we can.\nThere’s no point in worrying about it now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 85.23333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "なーんてみんなに言ってみたけど\n考えちゃうものはどうしようもないみたいでさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s what I told everyone‚ anyway.\nBut they didn’t seem to be able to get out of their own heads.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどなぁ……それで水遊びをしたと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So you kicked off a water fight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.66666666666669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 96.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 98.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "夏フェスだし、衣装も水着みたいなもんだしね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a summer festival‚ and our costumes are basically swimwear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "まずは琴乃ちゃんとすずにゃんから攻めたんだー\nそしたらみんな緊張がほぐれてきたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I targeted Kotono and Suzu-nyan first.\nThat helped loosen things up‚ but then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……だけど？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But then?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 112.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "……沙季ちゃんと渚ちゃんが二人がかりで攻めてきて\nそっから琴乃ちゃんとすずにゃんまで囲んできて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Saki and Nagisa got involved‚ attacking me as a team.\nBefore I knew it‚ Kotono and Suzu-nyan had surrounded me too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃と沙季まで加わるなんて意外な展開だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m surprised Kotono and Saki joined in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 128.23333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "それで慌てて逃げてきたってわけ\nあはは、楽しかったー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s why you’re on the run.\nHahaha! That was fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 133.166666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……はしゃぎ過ぎないようにな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Jeez… Just don’t get too carried away‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 136.466666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes",
      "startTime": 140.23333333333332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
